From: Nidhi Jain <nidhjain@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 25 Jul 2025 12:27:13 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL hostapd: Enhance Random Channel Change for
 AFC

Enhance random channel selection upon receiving the EVENT_AFC_RECEIVED.
Select a channel at random from the available set, giving priority to those
with higher EIRP values, and apply puncturing to the channel coding to
maximize the effective EIRP

1. Select a random channel when the event is received.
2. Select a random channel from those with the highest EIRP power.
3. Use both full and punctured channels to maximize EIRP power.
4. Check all SP combinations before transitioning to LPI.
5. Switch to the best power mode for the selected channel.
6. Trigger a Channel Switch Announcement (CSA) on the selected channel.

Feature: AFC
